title: Episode 32: UWGBpsych Student Orgs
itunes:author: UW-Green Bay Psychology Department
itunes:summary: In this episode, Ryan talks with Allee Schramm, Michaella Brickner, Michelle McChesney, and Annemarie Schwery about Psi Chi and the Psychology and Human Development Club (PsychHD) at UW-Green Bay.  They talk about why they got involved with the organizations, what they do in their different positions, and what they think they have gotten from their involvement.
